Cinemastar
=====================================================

Cinemastar is Home Video Server

Used
-----------------------------------------------------

 * ruby 1.9.3
 * sinatra
 * ffmpeg

Install
-----------------------------------------------------

install ffmpeg for homebrew

```sh
$ brew install FFmpeg
```

install bundler

```sh
$ gem install bundler
```

install gem

```sh
$ bundle install -path vendor/bundle
```

Setting
-----------------------------------------------------

### Write config/setting.yaml

```yaml
---
:movie_directory: /path/to/movie/directory
```

Start
------------------------------------------------------

```sh
$ bundle exec bin/server.rb
```

